@frittentheke hey, yep, just put the registry in the NO_PROXY, as a simple IP/hostname (no CIDR), and Voilà.

Please beware of the variable value length limitation (something like 256 chars or around that number) in case you want to push multiple values.

BTW, @rhatdan @mtrmac guess we might close that one, since the issue is more related to rhel7/8 golang version than skopeo itself.
